	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S[alutem] d[ico].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">In <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l648" cert="high">Rhetia</placeName> graves excitantur contentiones.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ipsissima causa esse videtur Servetanismus occultus.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ergo disputant contra symbola <placeName type="auto_name">Athanasii</placeName> et <placeName type="auto_name">Damasi</placeName> et ab his liberare volunt fideles etc.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quinque praecipui caeteris praeteritis fratribus <persName type="auto_name">Michaelem Angelum</persName> miserunt ad nos et <placeName ref="l28" cert="high">Basileam</placeName> cum quaestionibus valde suspectis.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scripsimus nos ad synodum, quae nunc habetur <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curia</placeName>, perplane causam, ut rei periculosae consulatur in tempore.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dehortati item sumus fratres illos, qui miserunt legatum, a studio novarum rerum et schismatum.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Expectamus iam, quid factum sit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Landgravius misit ad me tabellionem cum literis propter varias quaestiones.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Omnem operam offert et fidelem se in causa religionis ostendit sicuti et elector <persName type="auto_name">Palatinus</persName>.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex eius aula his diebus literas accepi significantes <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l749">Saxones</placeName> omnia tentare, ut abstrahant <placeName type="citizen_name">Palatinum</placeName>, hunc autem constanter manere ac acerbe a se abegisse solicitatores.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale aeternum cum omnibus tuis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Ohne Adresse.]<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><hi>Datum, Unterschrift und Adresse wurden vom Abschreiber durch einen Vermerk am Briefanfang ersetzt:</hi> Idem eidem. <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguro</placeName> Bernam. 4. iunii 1561.</note></note>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
